OL,3,CReform gains first MSP as Scottish
OL,4,CTory defects to Nigel Farage's party
OL,6,FReform UK has gained its first MSP in
OL,7,FScotland after Scottish Tory Graham
OL,8,FSimpson defected to join Nigel
OL,9,FFarage's party.
OL,11,FThe former frontbencher, who was first
OL,12,Felected in 2016, made the announcement
OL,13,Falongside Nigel Farage at a press
OL,14,Fconference in Broxburn, West Lothian.
OL,16,FAddressing the decision to leave the
OL,17,Fparty he joined at the age of 15,
OL,18,FGraham Simpson said it was a "wrench".
