OL,6,FThe new Reform MSP said: "It's fair to
OL,7,Fsay that some of you won't be
OL,8,Fsurprised to see me here, given that
OL,9,Fthe Scottish Tories have been touting
OL,10,Fmy name as a potential defector for
OL,11,Fmonths now.
OL,13,F"So today, I'm giving them what they
OL,14,Fwant, but perhaps not for the reasons
OL,15,Fthat they think.
OL,17,F"Leaving the party that I first joined
OL,18,Fwhen I was 15 is an enormous wrench,
OL,19,Fand I've been through a lot of soul
OL,20,Fsearching in the past few weeks."
