OL,6,FDuring his speech at the press
OL,7,Fconference he said he had decided
OL,8,Fearlier this year not to stand again
OL,9,Ffor the Scottish Tories, but it was
OL,10,Fnot until the past few weeks he had
OL,11,Fchosen to move to Reform UK.
OL,13,F"I watched Reform with interest and I
OL,14,Fsee the opportunity to help create
OL,15,Fsomething fresh here in Scotland, and
OL,16,Fit's clear that the voters agree in
OL,17,Fincreasing numbers," he told the press
OL,18,Fconference.
