OL,6,F"But just because a party is becoming
OL,7,Fpopular isn't a reason to join it,
OL,8,Fkeeping your job in Parliament isn't a
OL,9,Fgood enough reason either."
OL,11,FHe added: "Too many people feel let
OL,12,Fdown and ignored, they feel the system
OL,13,Fis against them, that the traditional
OL,14,Fparties don't even care about them.
OL,16,F"Save for some fine individual MSPs
OL,17,Facross parties, the political class is
OL,18,Fnot serving the people well."
