OL,11,FThe former Tory MSP told the press
OL,12,Fconference: "I've joined Reform
OL,13,Fbecause we have the chance to create
OL,14,Fsomething new, exciting and lasting
OL,15,Fthat puts the needs of people over the
OL,16,Fsystem, that asks what is going wrong
OL,17,Fhow we can fix it."
OL,19,FHe added he thought Reform could
OL,20,F"help" to remove the SNP from office
OL,21,Fafter 19 years in power.
