OL,6,FSimpson admitted he has been "uneasy"
OL,7,Fwith his decision to defect from the
OL,8,FScottish Conservatives, given he was
OL,9,Felected on the regional list at
OL,10,FHolyrood.
OL,12,FAt Holyrood, voters elect MSPs to both
OL,13,Fconstituencies and regional lists,
OL,14,Fwith votes in the regions being cast
OL,15,Ffor a party rather than an individual.
OL,17,FPut to him that Central Scotland
OL,18,Fregion voters backed the Tories rather
OL,19,Fthan him personally, Simpson said:
OL,20,F"Absolutely, you're right.
